{"tid":698382,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【一周必看】 fb keep咗你電話簿　輕輕一click刪除到","createTime":"2018-06-11T15:31:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-11T15:44:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"de0bb837435a9c865734f39673bb8bc28b58854b","tid":698382,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T15:31:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180611/20416676\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180611%2F20416676&d=MRtWvV%2BhC9yd2w7J3s%2Fj3k%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=41432605\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180611%2F20416676&h=83ff0600\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180611/20416676</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月11日 <br />\n<br />\n【一周必看】<br />\nfb keep咗你電話簿　輕輕一click刪除到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n誰偷走了我的電話簿？<br />\n<br />\n撰文︰盤古目<br />\n<br />\n個人資料是21世紀的金鑛，各家各戶網絡公司都扭盡六壬從用家身上攞料，攞得料多就生米變熟飯，你以後係我嘅人，任我魚肉。以至被圈養的我們亦落落大方；「我都冇秘密嘅，咪由得佢攞囉。」說的人落落大方，卻不見得會好順攤咁俾老婆睇佢相簿、電話簿或聊天對話。<br />\n<br />\n早前的Facebook私隱醜聞發生時香港人都似隔岸觀火，可能認為Facebook有的個人資料多極有限，頂多是我like邊個、上載咗啲相之類，但似乎不知Facebook這十幾年間，尤其透過手機應用，包括Facebook app、Facebook Messenger，不但管有你主動分享的文字、照片、位置等等作材料，好多用家「唔覺唔覺」在手機上啟動Facebook同步功能，在我們在手機安裝時那一窩蜂的設定中，經已佈局將我們電話中的電話簿甚至通話紀錄同步備份，電話簿、通話紀錄甚至SMS內容經已存到Facebook保管，你的一言一行、生活圈子，加上Facebook安插在其他網站上的like button，都是監察你日常喜好的探子，基本上已離不開朱克伯格手指罅。<br />\n<br />\n因應近日有關個人資料的要求，Facebook現提供下載個人資料途徑，大家可用電腦上 Facebook設定頁（<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/settings）下載，翻睇自己過往十多年來意想不到咁詳細的歷史，真係個心都離一離。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsettings%EF%BC%89%E4%B8%8B%E8%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E7%BF%BB%E7%9D%87%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E9%81%8E%E5%BE%80%E5%8D%81%E5%A4%9A%E5%B9%B4%E4%BE%86%E6%84%8F%E6%83%B3%E4%B8%8D%E5%88%B0%E5%92%81%E8%A9%B3%E7%B4%B0%E7%9A%84%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2%EF%BC%8C%E7%9C%9F%E4%BF%82%E5%80%8B%E5%BF%83%E9%83%BD%E9%9B%A2%E4%B8%80%E9%9B%A2%E3%80%82&d=MRtWvV%2BhC9yd2w7J3s%2Fj3k%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=596b895d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/settings）下載，翻睇自己過往十多年來意想不到咁詳細的歷史，真係個心都離一離。</a><br />\n<br />\n有人見到可能晴天霹靂，但話唔埋有人發現之前壞電話、唔見電話時冇咗的電話資料竟然冰封於此，反而感激Facebook，以身相許。<br />\n<br />\n大家不妨到以下兩個Facebook連結望望，睇吓Facebook有冇keep到你的電話簿及通話紀錄，之後亦可到呢兩個app的設定中關閉通訊錄同步功能。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFacebook電話紀錄<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/mobile/facebook/contacts/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmobile%2Ffacebook%2Fcontacts%2F&d=MRtWvV%2BhC9yd2w7J3s%2Fj3k%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=d9fbc16e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/mobile/facebook/contacts/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFacebook Messengers電話紀錄<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/mobile/messenger/contacts/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmobile%2Fmessenger%2Fcontacts%2F&d=MRtWvV%2BhC9yd2w7J3s%2Fj3k%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=3d2eef2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/mobile/messenger/contacts/</a>  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n【一周必看】路邊芒果不要貪　吸晒廢氣農藥食咗就慘<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n【一周必看】光頭叔大戰打尖青年　爆缸血染油麻地"},{"pid":"92a318a937e4feb3886500cb6ac586da1ad38085","tid":698382,"uid":39218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T15:44:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/11/234423_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F11%2F234423_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=1bdbd7b3&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}